    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this breathtaking, mint-condition gem! Every inch of this vehicle has been meticulously maintained, looking and driving exactly like the day it left the showroom. From its flawless exterior to its pristine interior, this is a rare opportunity to own a car that truly defines perfection.",
